Cadastro de Clientes

Clientes:{{evento.cliente}}

Equipamento:{{evento.equipamento}}

import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-eventos', templateUrl: './eventos.component.html', styleUrls: ['./eventos.component.css'] }) export class EventosComponent implements OnInit { public eventos: any; constructor(private http: HttpClient) { } ngOnInit(): void{ this.getEventos(); } public getEventos(): void { this.http.get('https://localhost:5001/Evento').subscri( response => this.eventos = response, error => console.log(error) ); } }
